Company Overview of HGGC Fund II, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
HGGC Fund II, L.P. specializes in mid-market buyout investments. It seeks to invest in North America. The fund also makes co-investments. It prefers to make control investments and seeks majority stake in the companies.


